\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The perfect webinar email sequence\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 From the first webinar invite email to the final follow up, each message in your sequence has a job to do. Here's a walkthrough of the essential emails that move people from curious clickers to engaged webinar attendees.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 1. Webinar Invite email\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67f6cdc3b593cbc3ffdaaf91_d10b0482-0811-49e3-a360-be65fac827c6.png \width27200 \height43200 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: You\'92re invited: The best Calendly plan for your sales goals\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Your webinar invitation email is the spark that gets the fire going. This is where you introduce the webinar topic, give a compelling brief description, and link to the webinar landing page with a strong call to action to register.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your invitation email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Lead with value\'97what will they walk away with? Make the subject line attention-grabbing but clear, keep the body scannable, and feature a prominent registration link. Mention the webinar date, include the calendar link, and make sure the design looks clean across devices.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 2. Registration confirmation email\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe90449fcdf0c824e791c4_05a1ff28-9b75-4fba-89ef-71fe305d04a4.png \width41640 \height18440 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: Masterclass with Clifton Sellers\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Once someone registers, hit them with a confirmation email right away. This builds trust, reduces uncertainty, and sets the tone for a smooth attendee experience.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your confirmation email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Thank them for registering and clearly repeat the event details: webinar title, date, time, and webinar link. Include a calendar event download or calendar link so they can save it instantly. If you\'92re feeling fancy, add a short intro to the speaker or tease the agenda.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 3. First reminder\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe9044b2c4ed797668d2f0_198b315e-2a74-42a3-aac8-275da0dfb349.png \width34960 \height39920 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: See you tomorrow \'95 Mastering B2B Lifecycle Marketing\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The first webinar reminder email is your \'93just a heads up\'94 email, ideally sent one day before the webinar date. It\'92s a friendly, timely way to rekindle interest and make sure your upcoming webinar doesn\'92t get lost in the shuffle.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your first reminder email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Remind them what they signed up for, when it\'92s happening, and why it\'92s worth showing up. Reiterate the webinar topic, tease 1\'962 valuable insights, and drop the webinar link again. You can also mention what kind of webinar content they can expect\'97Q&A, demo, or bonus perks.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 4. Second reminder\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe9044aa2b984c05d7a489_573170bf-d8d6-4171-965a-8b41b9fd1b5f.png \width31960 \height40640 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: STARTING SOON \'95 Mastering B2B Lifecycle Marketing\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 This is your quick reminder to make sure they\'92re still on board and ready. Sent one hour before the webinar, it gives attendees time to wrap up what they\'92re doing and prep for your session.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your second reminder email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Keep the message clear and confident: \'93Your webinar starts in 1 hour.\'94 Reinforce the event details, drop the calendar event one more time, and make the call to action obvious with a bold \'93Join Event\'94 or \'93Access Link\'94 button.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Third and final reminder email\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe9044fd904384e9471635_d75b15ee-2429-4162-bdec-78578909263a.png \width31040 \height39800 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: Starting NOW \'95 Mastering B2B Lifecycle Marketing5. Thank you email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Sent just minutes before showtime, this final webinar reminder email is the digital equivalent of opening the doors. It helps get people in the room\'97especially those who forgot or are running late.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your third reminder email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Short, sharp, and high-energy. \'93We\'92re live\'97grab your coffee and click below to join!\'94 Make sure the webinar link is front and center. Emojis or playful copy can help it stand out in busy inboxes and increase attendance during those last few moments.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 5. Thank you email\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe90430efefc6807ea3b1b_abe2345d-d8c4-40fb-b5af-2aeb415984d4.png \width17780 \height43200 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: Email is still "top dog"\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Your thank you email keeps the conversation going post-event. It\'92s also your chance to make a great second impression\'97especially if the attendee didn\'92t get everything they hoped for live.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your thank you email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Send it within an hour of the event wrapping up. Thank them for attending, briefly recap the webinar topic, and let them know when to expect the webinar recording. If applicable, link to a brief survey to collect feedback and improve future online events.\
Personalize this email depending on whether they actually attended\'97acknowledge their presence or gently say, \'93Sorry we missed you!\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 6. Webinar recording\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fbf9d3500311aa2405993e_14d6540f-8412-4930-a993-804152ea5391.png \width23460 \height43200 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: Thank you for joining us for our January Coffee Chat\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 This one\'92s crucial\'97many people register and never attend. Don\'92t let the relationship end there. Your webinar recording email helps keep late registrants and no-shows engaged.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your webinar recording email\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Start with a \'93Here\'92s your recording link\'94 email subject line, then include a short summary of the session\'92s best moments. Add links to relevant resources like blog posts, templates, or guides mentioned during the event.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li800\fi-800\ri800\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \uc0\u55357 \u56481  Personalize the message based on attendance\'97if they were there live, acknowledge it and frame the email as a recap; if they missed it, frame it as a second chance to catch up. Keep your call to action simple and aligned to your next funnel step.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 7. Webinar follow up and marketing emails\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 {{\NeXTGraphic 67fe9044d8546f59275df724_d3296b39-41af-42a3-aea2-929413167416.png \width12820 \height43200 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}Ỳ}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
Subject line: Check out this month's roster of value-packed events\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 These emails help you capitalize on all the interest you\'92ve built. Whether it\'92s pointing folks to future events, a next webinar, or product content, your follow up email sequence closes the loop.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa319\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 \strokec2 How to nail your marketing emails\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf0 \strokec2 Send your first webinar follow up email a few days after the event. Use it to segment users by behavior\'97who attended, who clicked, who converted\'97and send tailored messages.\
Promote future webinars, link to a landing page for more events, or highlight new features that relate to the webinar topic. Keep things conversational and action-focused.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Complete webinar email sequence example of customer.io\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Below is a breakdown of a complete webinar email sequence from {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://customer.io/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 Customer.io}}. It\'92s a great example of a thoughtful, well-paced campaign that includes every key message from the initial webinar invite email to the post webinar email follow-up. Let\'92s take a look at what they did and why it works.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

